verses.text: Unto \w the|strong="H5921"\w* end, \w a|strong="H5921"\w* psalm \w for|strong="H5921"\w* \w David|strong="H1732"\w*, \w to|strong="H5921"\w* bring \w to|strong="H5921"\w* remembrance \w that|strong="H1732"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* Lord saved \w him|strong="H5921"\w*.

\w O|strong="H5315"\w* \w God|strong="H0430"\w*, \w come|strong="H0935"\w* \w to|strong="H0935"\w* \w my|strong="H0935"\w* assistance; \w O|strong="H5315"\w* Lord, \w make|strong="H3588"\w* haste \w to|strong="H0935"\w* \w help|strong="H3467"\w* \w me|strong="H5315"\w*.
Let \w them|strong="H0935"\w* \w be|strong="H0369"\w* confounded \w and|strong="H0935"\w* ashamed \w that|strong="H4325"\w* seek \w my|strong="H0935"\w* soul:

Let \w them|strong="H7121"\w* \w be|strong="H0430"\w* turned backward, \w and|strong="H0430"\w* blush \w for|strong="H7121"\w* shame \w that|strong="H7121"\w* desire evils \w to|strong="H0430"\w* \w me|strong="H7121"\w*: Let \w them|strong="H7121"\w* \w be|strong="H0430"\w* presently turned \w away|strong="H3615"\w* blushing \w for|strong="H7121"\w* shame \w that|strong="H7121"\w* say \w to|strong="H0430"\w* \w me|strong="H7121"\w*: Tis well, tis well.

\w Let|strong="H3808"\w* all \w that|strong="H0834"\w* \w seek|strong="H3808"\w* thee rejoice \w and|strong="H7725"\w* \w be|strong="H3808"\w* glad \w in|strong="H7725"\w* thee; \w and|strong="H7725"\w* \w let|strong="H3808"\w* \w such|strong="H0834"\w* \w as|strong="H0834"\w* love thy salvation say always: \w The|strong="H0834"\w* Lord \w be|strong="H3808"\w* magnified.

\w But|strong="H3808"\w* \w I|strong="H3045"\w* \w am|strong="H0430"\w* needy \w and|strong="H0430"\w* poor; \w O|strong="H0859"\w* \w God|strong="H0430"\w*, help \w me|strong="H4480"\w*. Thou art \w my|strong="H3045"\w* helper \w and|strong="H0430"\w* \w my|strong="H3045"\w* deliverer: \w O|strong="H0859"\w* Lord, \w make|strong="H3045"\w* \w no|strong="H3808"\w* delay.
